To support the Finance &amp; Accounting Team Lead in daily finance operations including but not limited to Accounts Receivables &amp; Invoicing.

This is a maternity cover role for 7 months, which is subjected to renewal.

Responsibilities
  Daily Accounts receivables updates
  Debt collecting ( via calls &amp; emails)
  Matching of supporting documents and resolving customer invoices issues
  Generate and send out monthly statement of accounts
  Any Ad hoc task assigned by supervisor